@startuml seq-20-feedback
' 序列图20：提交反馈
title 提交反馈序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "help.js" as Front
participant "FeedbackController" as Ctrl
participant "FeedbackService" as Svc
participant "FeedbackMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 填写反馈类型/内容/联系方式
User -> Front: 点击"提交"
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/feedback/submit(userId,type,content,contact)
Ctrl -> Svc: submit(feedback)
Svc -> Mapper: insert(feedback)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO feedback(user_id,type,content,contact,create_time)
DB --> Mapper: feedback_id
Mapper --> Svc: feedback_id
Svc --> Ctrl: feedback_id
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front --> User: 提示提交成功,感谢反馈

@enduml
